OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,FThe mum of a teenage boy from Southend
OL,8,Fwho died after taking drugs in Ibiza
OL,9,Fis warning other young people about
OL,10,Fthe risks.
OL,12,FRyan Long, 18, was on holiday with
OL,13,Ffriends in July 2025 when he died.
OL,15,FRyan was airlifted to Palma hospital
OL,16,Fwhere he spent five days in intensive
OL,17,Fcare, but doctors couldn't save him.
OL,19,FRyan's inquest identified MDMA and
OL,20,Fcocaine as the cause of death in his
OL,21,Fmedical report.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,FHis mum Angie now wants to keep her
OL,8,Fson's memory alive by ensuring that no
OL,9,Fother family has to go through what
OL,10,Fthey did.
OL,12,FShe has handed out leaflets and beer
OL,13,Fmats to local pubs, warning punters of
OL,14,Fthe dangers of taking drugs, and is
OL,15,Fnow taking Ryan's story into local
OL,16,Fschools and colleges too.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Ms Long
OL,19,Fsaid: "Ryan obviously thought he was
OL,20,Finvincible, it wouldn't happen to him,
OL,21,Fas a lot of youngsters do.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,F"They're in these situations that they
OL,8,Fgo clubbing, festivals, concerts,
OL,9,Fwhatever it is, and they take
OL,10,Fsomething.
OL,12,F"When this first happened, a lot of
OL,13,Fparents reached out to us with the
OL,14,Fsame thing, their kids just don't come
OL,15,Fhome and it has got to stop."
OL,17,FShe continued: "The awareness needs to
OL,18,Fbe out there for the youngsters to
OL,19,Fknow the risks and warning signs for
OL,20,Ftheir friends to look out for.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,F"If no parent has to go through this,
OL,8,Fit would mean Ryan's legacy lives on,
OL,9,Fand that is the whole point of this is
OL,10,Fkeeping his name out there and for
OL,11,Fnobody to forget this story."
OL,13,FMs Long added that said she warned
OL,14,FRyan about taking drugs before he went
OL,15,Faway, referencing the story of Leah
OL,16,FBetts, who died in November 1995 after
OL,17,Ftaking ecstasy at her 18th birthday
OL,18,Fparty.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,FShe said: "That put the frighteners on
OL,8,Fme (what happened to Leah Betts), and
OL,9,FI wanted my boys to know her story -
OL,10,Fthe dangers around drugs and obviously
OL,11,Fthe consequences, showing that it can
OL,12,Feasily happen to anybody.
OL,14,F"I hoped by sharing that story with my
OL,15,Fboys that it would have the same
OL,16,Feffect it had on me, but sadly it
OL,17,Fnever did."
OL,19,FMs Long said: "He (Ryan) was so
OL,20,Flooking forward to going to Ibiza.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@KO]{D@OOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,F"This one was special because it was
OL,8,Fgoing to be around the club scene,
OL,9,Fwhich he'd obviously shown an interest
OL,10,Fin with DJing and I'd spoken to him
OL,11,Fthe night he landed and again
OL,12,Fexpressed, be careful!"
OL,14,F"He knew the risks and I had obviously
OL,15,Freminded him of the risks before they
OL,16,Fwent.
OL,26,@tD@WO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,F"The following morning... I got a
OL,8,Fphone call from his friend, and I
OL,9,Fcould hear the sirens in the
OL,10,Fbackground, and he said Ryan was in
OL,11,Fthe back of an ambulance being worked
OL,12,Fon and obviously was in a very bad way.
OL,14,FJoni Thompson, from drug and alcohol
OL,15,Fsupport charity Open Road, emphasised
OL,16,Fhow young people shouldn't be afraid
OL,17,Fto speak out if they have concerns
OL,18,Faround drugs.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,FShe said: "I think the message to
OL,8,Fyoung people is, you know, please
OL,9,Fdon't be afraid to say something.
OL,11,F"If you are out with friends and
OL,12,Fsomebody has taken something, we want
OL,13,Fto help those individuals.
OL,15,F"So please, you're not going to get
OL,16,Finto trouble, you're not going to be
OL,17,Fin trouble for telling somebody, it's
OL,18,Fabout getting the help.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781606875
OL,3,CMum of teenager who died after taking
OL,4,Cdrugs on holiday in Ibiza warns of
OL,5,Crisks
OL,7,F"But I think it's also about
OL,8,Funderstanding the impact that that's
OL,9,Fhad on those young people that were
OL,10,Fthere with Ryan at the time, having to
OL,11,Fmake that very difficult phone call,
OL,12,Fhaving to speak to Angie, tell her
OL,13,Fwhat's happened.
OL,15,F"And for some of them, they're still
OL,16,Fstruggling with the outcome and the
OL,17,Faftermath of that incident, so I think
OL,18,Fit's acknowledging that it's not just
OL,19,Fthe family, it's the wider, wider
OL,20,Fcommunity that are affected as well."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
